{"entity":{"id":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","type":"chapter","slug":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","label":"Amos.5","rawId":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","book":{"id":"rec5weNA8SDG9Gk1x","type":"book","slug":"amos","label":"Amos","subtitle":"Minor Prophets","count":146,"description":"9 chapters, 89 people, 39 places"}},"stats":{"verses":27,"people":2,"places":4,"events":1},"nodes":[{"id":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Amos.5","slug":"amos_5","score":27},{"id":"rec5weNA8SDG9Gk1x","type":"book","group":"book","label":"Amos","slug":"amos","score":146},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":11},{"id":"rechuDYJoK32gmrME","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Joseph (son of Jacob)","slug":"joseph_1710","score":2},{"id":"recJK76HLZSOzxTWW","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Bethel (of Palestine)","slug":"bethel_202","score":2},{"id":"rectrAkGtrZH5LMp8","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Beersheba","slug":"beersheba_170","score":1},{"id":"recdm9AlLF01lFAfP","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Gilgal","slug":"gilgal_476","score":1},{"id":"recR67sC02MfTx4al","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Damascus","slug":"damascus_322","score":1},{"id":"rec0MJooZFfHsxW1N","type":"event","group":"event","label":"Prophecies of Amos","slug":"event-205","score":27}],"links":[{"source":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","target":"rec5weNA8SDG9Gk1x","label":"part of"},{"source":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","target":"rechuDYJoK32gmrME","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","target":"recJK76HLZSOzxTWW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","target":"rectrAkGtrZH5LMp8","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","target":"recdm9AlLF01lFAfP","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","target":"recR67sC02MfTx4al","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec45SFTOMoSlxow2","target":"rec0MJooZFfHsxW1N","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"reccKkvTH7mdGj1Tl","ref":"Amos.5.1","text":"Hear ye this word which I take up against you, even a lamentation, O house of Israel.","year":-787},{"id":"rec2LLQDd2hXmsJ8o","ref":"Amos.5.2","text":"The virgin of Israel is fallen; she shall no more rise: she is forsaken upon her land; there is none to raise her up.","year":-787},{"id":"recWHd6bmENjaE3Ou","ref":"Amos.5.3","text":"For thus saith the Lord GOD; The city that went out by a thousand shall leave an hundred, and that which went forth by an hundred shall leave ten, to the house of Israel.","year":-787},{"id":"recX7O7YupkHTdKHD","ref":"Amos.5.4","text":"For thus saith the LORD unto the house of Israel, Seek ye me, and ye shall live:","year":-787},{"id":"recTG6GHSUOfRtC8D","ref":"Amos.5.5","text":"But seek not Bethel, nor enter into Gilgal, and pass not to Beersheba: for Gilgal shall surely go into captivity, and Bethel shall come to nought.","year":-787},{"id":"recnnGJDnGF67lEop","ref":"Amos.5.6","text":"Seek the LORD, and ye shall live; lest he break out like fire in the house of Joseph, and devour it, and there be none to quench it in Bethel.","year":-787},{"id":"recSyAybmJ7j9w9ci","ref":"Amos.5.7","text":"Ye who turn judgment to wormwood, and leave off righteousness in the earth,","year":-787},{"id":"recs7hyKTUxhYrROn","ref":"Amos.5.8","text":"Seek him that maketh the seven stars and Orion, and turneth the shadow of death into the morning, and maketh the day dark with night: that calleth for the waters of the sea, and poureth them out upon the face of the earth: The LORD is his name:","year":-787}]}
